Different social media platforms serve different purposes and audiences. By understanding the SMM process, you can select the platforms that best fit your business needs and target audience. Whether it’s Facebook for broad reach, LinkedIn for B2B connections, or Instagram for visual content, choosing the right platforms ensures that your social media efforts are optimized for success.

 
