 What is included in WordPress development services?
 Our services typically include custom theme development, plugin integration, responsive design, performance optimization, security enhancements, and ongoing maintenance and support.
 
 
 How long does it take to develop a WordPress website?
 The timeline for developing a WordPress website depends on the project’s complexity and scope. On average, it can take anywhere from a few weeks to a few months. We’ll provide a detailed timeline based on your specific needs.
 
 
 Can I update and manage my WordPress site myself?
 Yes, WordPress is designed to be user-friendly, allowing you to easily update content, manage pages, and make changes without needing extensive technical knowledge. We also offer training and support to help you get comfortable with managing your site.
 
 
 What should I expect during the WordPress development process?
 You can expect a structured process including an initial consultation, project planning, design and development, testing, and launch. We also provide post-launch support to ensure everything runs smoothly.
 
 
 Do you offer support after the website is launched?
 Yes, we provide ongoing support and maintenance services to address any issues, perform updates, and make necessary adjustments to keep your website functioning optimally.
 
 
