 How can I determine the right support plan for my business?
 The right support plan depends on your business needs, website complexity, and the level of service required. We offer a free consultation to assess your specific requirements and develop a customized support plan that aligns with your goals and budget.
 
 
 What is the response time for support requests?
 Our response time depends on the urgency and complexity of the support request. We prioritize urgent issues to minimize downtime and ensure quick resolution. For non-urgent requests, we provide timely updates and work efficiently to address your needs.
 
 
 How often will my website receive maintenance and updates?
 The frequency of maintenance and updates depends on your support plan and specific requirements. Regular maintenance typically includes software updates, backups, and performance checks. We tailor our maintenance schedule to ensure your website remains secure and optimized.
 
 
 What if I need support outside of regular business hours?
 We understand that issues can arise outside of regular business hours. Depending on your support plan, we may offer extended or 24/7 support to address urgent issues promptly. Contact us to discuss available options for after-hours support.
 
 
 How do I get started with Olympia Marketing’s support services?
