 - Includes everything in Accelerator Basic
 - Social Media Ad Setup
 - Custom CRM Setup + School Optimizations- Brand Refresh (Logo, Corporate ID, Brochures)- Customized School Ad Books- Marketing Plan Development- Local PR Push- CRM Coaching- Enhanced and Ongoing Local SEO Optimization (Boost Pack, NAP Submission)- Private School Marketing Group- Managed Content Marketing Campaigns- Enhanced Quarterly Zoom Calls with Performance Insights
 
 
 
 
