 The Skin Care Academy of Florida, founded by Laura Lorusso, is dedicated to empowering the next generation of skincare professionals. Laura Lorusso’s journey into esthetician education began after spending over two decades as a licensed esthetician, spa director and a teacher at another local institution. Despite her extensive expertise in skincare, Laura was concerned with the quality of the education in the Esthetics field and decided to take it head on – founding her Company in 2020 during Covid. Unfortunately, Laura faced challenges when it came to running & expanding her school’s enrollment – particularly when it came to attracting and onboarding new students.

 
