 A Customized Plan
with the Beauty School Accelerator Max

 
 ## Working With Olympia Marketing

 
 We started with our consultative selling process, getting to know Laura and her business, all the ins-and-outs of everything going on including existing marketing & advertising efforts as well as her current revenue and her plans for 2024 and 2025. We then did a review of their online presence, and our team got to work formulating a plan. Within 2 initial calls Laura was ready to sign up! Laura and our team determined that our premiere Beauty School Accelerator Max package would be implemented.**Our service offering at this level is VERY comprehensive and included the following:**

 
 #### Website
A brand new, gorgeous website that was simple, easy to use, and converted far greater than her existing homemade site.

 
 #### Brochures & Brand
