Laura and the Olympia Marketing team worked together to implement our Custom
Beauty School CRM and develop a custom sales & marketing automation process.

 
 From Low Traffic to High Demand

 
 ## The Website
Transformation of The Skin Care Academy
 
 The Skin Care Academy of Florida partnered with Olympia Marketing to transform their website and significantly improve its performance. Previously, despite its visual appeal, the site struggled with converting visitors into student leads. After a strategic overhaul, the website experienced a 200% increase in student inquiries within the first 60 days and a 600% rise in monthly leads by the end of 2024. The site now ranks at the top for all relevant keywords, achieved the #1 spot in the GMB map pack for searches, and boasts a 1500% improvement in conversion rates, jumping from 1% to over 15%. This optimization has resulted in an average lead value of $1,000,000 per month, with SEO alone driving about 20 leads per month, adding $150,000 in student value. The redesigned site now consistently drives new student enrollments, securing the academy’s position as a leading institution in skincare education.

 
 
 
 
