## Google Local Service Ads Frequently Asked Questions

- [Frequently Asked Questions](#frequently-asked-questions)

- [How do I set up a Google Business Profile Account?](#how-do-i-set-up-a-google-business-profile-account)

- [What’s crucial when verifying my profile?](#whats-crucial-when-verifying-my-profile)

