We currently rank in the Google Map Pack and hold the #3 position for the exact term: **SWFL marketing agency**. This is in direct competition with agencies that have been in business for over 30 years and have dozens of staff.

How did we do it? A deep understanding of:

- [Local SEO](https://olympiamarketing.com/marketing-advertising-services/digital-marketing/local-seo/)

