This is what separates Olympia from every other **SWFL marketing agency** out there: we actually care about results and relationships.

## Beauty School Marketing: A Perfect Example

One of our top-performing verticals is beauty schools. Through our GlowPro division, we’ve helped schools double and even triple their enrollment by leveraging:

- Google Ads

